Save to `articles/YYYY-MM-DD-<descriptive-slug>.md`:

```markdown
---
title: "Article Title"
source_url: "https://..."
date: "YYYY-MM-DD"
words_used: ["word1", "word2", ...]
difficulty: "Intermediate-Advanced"
topic: "Technology & Society"
target_language: "{{TARGET}}"
---

# Article Title

[Full article body with **bolded** target words]

